  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/365",
  "title": "Issue with Selector rendering",
  "body": "On Firefox 41.0.2, I get this weird issue on a value selection where it displays: \n- The selected option\n- The first option for a fraction of a sec\n- The selected option back again\n\n![selector bug](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5095856/10756357/d62e3f00-7ca3-11e5-9eae-a754f518dcc6.gif)\n\nIt seems like `render` is only called once, but I believe the issue might be caused by the replacement of the select in the DOM.\n",
